**File Structure:**
```
/
├── index.html              # Main HTML file
├── README                  # Project overview (this file)
├── CODE_FUNCTIONS_README.md # Code documentation and guides
├── School_info_snhs.js     # JavaScript functionality
└── images/                 # Image assets
    ├── snhs-logo.jpg       # School logo
    └── principal-image.png # Principal photo
```

**How to modify:**

